Concierge Log In Cart Search Bid Concierge Toggle Concierge FAQs Privacy Policy Terms & Conditions Terms of Sale Shipping Private Sales Is a Private Sale the same as an Auction? No, Private Sales are different from Auctions in that there is no bidding, and purchases are made Any registered customer is welcome to How do I access the Private Limited Sale? Once you successfully register with JOOPITER, you will have able to access the beautiful jewelry and gemstones—which can be fashioned into jewelry by commissioning Lorraine Schwartz—directly. How do I purchase a Private Sale lot? Making a purchase is Prospective buyers can contact JOOPITER Sales in these easy ways: Submit an enquiry on Email Is there a buyer’s premium for Private Sale lots? There is no buyer’s premium for Private Sale The accepted price, plus applicable taxes and shipping charges, is what you How do I pay if my offer is accepted? You will receive an email with a link to purchase with one of our available payment Auctions What do I need to bid on an auction? Bidding is All you need to do is create an account, verify your phone number, and verify your identity through From there you can bid on any The identity verification flow is available through signup or your account You are ready to bid when your JOOPITER card turns Is there a buyers premium? There is a % buyers premium on all auction You will see the buyers premium calculated before you place your What are the conditions of sale? You can find the JOOPITER Conditions of Sale here How do I know the items are authentic? All items are appraised and Professional reports for all jewelry and watches can be provided upon request to JOOPITER Concierge and will be delivered to the auction Can I cancel a bid? Once a bid is placed, the only way to cancel it is to reach out to JOOPITER We cannot guarantee that a bid cancellation request will be Can I see the objects in person before I bid? JOOPITER will produce exhibitions of the objects for private and public Please join the mailing list for exhibition What methods can I use to bid? You can place your bid on Bidding and Auction Close How does a maximum bid work? By entering a maximum bid amount, our system will automatically bid for you until your maximum bid is reached, saving you the time of having to bid You tell us your absolute maximum price by entering the figure in the max bid’ box on the lot page, and click place bid . The auction engine will place your bids at the next available increment to keep you in the lead, but only up to your max price and never any If the bidding passes your maximum amount, then you may miss out on winning the However, we ll email you to let you know so you can increase your max bid if you What is a “closing period”? When the auction timer reaches zero, the auction enters the closing period for 2 The closing period is the final two minutes of an If someone bids in the last two minutes, and if their bid exceeds all others, the auction will automatically extend by an additional two Each time a winning bidder is outbid at any point during the closing period, the auction extends for another two For example, the Lot 1 closing period is 9 :02 AM If a new high bid is entered between 9:00 AM and 9:02 AM the closing period will extend for 2 minutes from the time of the This will continue indefinitely during the closing period with each new high bid until a winning bidder is not outbid and two minutes Is there a minimum amount I can bid on an auction? All auctions have a minimum bid requirement, this will appear as the next increment in the bid increment What is a Reserve Price? A reserve price is the minimum amount the seller will accept as a winning The reserve price itself is never disclosed, however the auction will indicate whether the reserve price has been met or If the reserve price has not been met when the auction closes, the item will remain with the Auction Payment How do I pay if I win an auction? Once the auction closes, you will receive an email with a link to purchase with one of our available payment What methods of payment do you support? JOOPITER supports credit card payments up to $100,000, wire transfers, and crypto How do I pay with wire transfer? Once you win an auction, you will receive an email about the auction If you would like to pay by wire transfer, please reach out to and we will be happy to Auction Shipping and Delivery When can I arrange my shipping details for an auction? You will receive a shipping quote from our carrier at time of Once you checkout, our partners will handle all your shipping Joopiter concierge is also available to assist with any special If your shipment fails to provide a quote, JOOPITER concierge will be in touch to arrange shipping Can I arrange my own carrier for delivery? Yes, please reach out to JOOPITER concierge to arrange a pick Additional verification steps Merchandise and Retail How do I purchase JOOPITER products and merchandise? JOOPITER merch is sold on a fir

Our partners Hundreds of communities including Whatâs a Kudos? A Kudos is a digital token representing involvement within an Education certification Completing a workshop Education access pass Speaking at a conference Team shoutouts Welcoming a new teammate Winning an award Attending a community townhall Why use Kudos? Giving Kudos is a great way to recognize and reward amazing feats or projects within your They serve as a badge of honor that commemorates the pride and joy behind a Individuals can claim Kudos to build out an , , authentic history of their Yes, we cover gas! How it works Step 1: Create the Kudos Fill in the details of the Kudos youâre We use these details to generate a Kudos that uniquely the achievement youâre Raised $500k to fund amazing web3 project woo Crazy amazing effort by this team, two week hustle Lorem ipsum dolor sit â¤ï¸ via Step 2: Send the Kudos Send the Kudos by specifiying the recipients, tagging them on Discord, giving them a link, or generating a QR Step 3: Claim the Kudos Others can mint the token on our site and celebrate their achievement with you! Share this link with your teammates so they can claim their kudos Create Kudos - FAQ Do I need to get my Kudos approved before I can issue them? Nope! Once you are onboarded as an admin, you can mint a Kudos for anyone, at any time, with any look! Unlike other products, we do not have a review process for the NFTs you give out to your Really? You cover all the gas? Yes we do! Our goal is to provide the best experience possible for creators and Weâve decided to cover the gas so that users donât have to worry about buying MATIC in order to use I received a Kudos containing false What should I do? We encourage everyone to not claim an incorrect Kudos as it devalues the authenticity of your current collection and promotes bad But itâs your wallet, your Why mint the contribution as a Soulbound (non-transferable) token? Imagine our world as a village with a big bulletin board that tracks all the things people have Minting your contribution into a Soulbound token is like adding a record of your work onto that board for everyone to admire, with a guarantee that this record wasnât bought and canât be Can I mint a Kudos for myself? No teammates? No Give yourself a Kudos for doing something After all that hard work, give yourself a pat on the back! If you were a part of a team, make sure to include yourself! Which chain are you on? Polygon! Weâve made it a top priority to make sure gas prices donât become a hurdle to giving out In the future we may add the option to bridge the token to other chains (such as Ethereum Mainnet). How do I get involved or give feedback? Weâre on a mission to enable the Contributor Say hi to us on Discord or follow our Twitter! Want to directly connect with us? We believe that many (if not most) chemicals, ingredients, and materials should be made by microbes . This is the future potential of biomanufacturing: To build a sustainable economy that is supplied with green, renewable To arrive at this future, we are using synthetic biology to turn microbes into production From chemicals and cosmetics to food ingredients and fragrances, our microbes have a distinct advantage because they’re unlike anything the industry has ever There are estimated to be ~1 trillion microbial species on Earth: what an incredible We find the best microbes that nature has to offer , sourcing them from diverse, wild Their inherent traits mean huge cost savings in biomanufacturing and access to new categories of products and Teaming with innovative partners, we then help to harness the potential in these Through our proprietary technology, we have the unique ability to develop these new microbes and put them to Come explore the microbial universe with us and unleash its potential on your Subscribe We’d love to keep in touch! They are all decoupled from your UI components and business logic , so they never keep you from customizing your UI or coding your own refine seamlessly works with any custom design or UI framework you favor . For convenience, it ships with integrations for Ant Design System , Material UI , Mantine , and Chakra UI . Use cases ​ refine shines on applications like admin panels , dashboards and internal tools . Thanks to SSR support , refine can also power applications like storefronts . Key Features ​ ⚙️ , setup with a single CLI command 🔌 Connectors for + backend services including REST API , GraphQL , NestJs CRUD , Airtable , Strapi , Strapi v4 , Strapi GraphQL , Supabase , Hasura , Nhost , Appwrite , Firebase , Directus and Altogic 🌐 SSR support with or Remix ⚛ Perfect state management & mutations with React Query 🔀 Advanced routing with any router library of your choice 🔐 Providers for seamless authentication and access control flows ⚡ support for live applications 📄 Easy audit logs & document versioning 💬 Support for any i18n framework 💪 , robust architecture ✅ Full test coverage Community ​ refine has a very friendly community and we are always happy to help you get started: Join the Discord Community – it is the easiest way to get help, all questions are usually answered in about GitHub Discussions – ask anything about the project or give Contributing – learn how to contribute refine Guest Technical Writer Program – join the program and become a blog writer for Roadmap ​ You can find Refine s Public Roadmap here!
